==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thornback
<hw>Thorn"back`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A European skate (<spn>Raia clavata</spn>)
having thornlike spines on its back.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The large European spider crab or
king crab (<spn>Maia squinado</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thornbill</ent>⟦br⟧
